snippet.title: Evergreen Beta Trailer
snippet.description: Thanks for watching! Evergreen is being worked on by a dedicated team of developers who are adding features and content to make it the best experience possible. Follow the team on facebook (https://www.facebook.com/siegeslothgames/) or Twitter (https://twitter.com/SiegeSlothGames) to stay up to date on the development.
